neuragenix.dao
Class DALMasterQuery

java.lang.Object
  neuragenix.dao.DALMasterQuery
Direct Known Subclasses:
DALInsertQuery, DALSelectQuery, DALUpdateQuery
public abstract class DALMasterQuery
extends java.lang.Object

This object is the parent class for the DALInsertQuery, DALUpdateQuery and DALSelectQuery. It sets the domains, fields and where causes for it's children objects.
